[[Image:YHN Cover.JPG|thumb|''Your Health Now'']] {{Italic title}} '''''Your Health Now''''' was a free, bi-monthly health magazine provided by [[Merck & Co.|Merck & Co., Inc.]].<ref name=bwire/> The magazine was launched in September 2005<ref name=bwire>{{cite news|title=Merck Launches New Health Magazine, Your Health Now|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20050921005078/en/Merck-Launches-Health-Magazine-Health-Publication-Driven|accessdate=13 December 2015|work=BusinessWire|date=21 September 2005}}</ref> and was available by mail, online, and in doctors’ offices. The magazine was headquartered in [[Whitehouse Station, New Jersey]].<ref name=prn/>
Every issue included articles on various health topics, updates on patient assistance programs, an “Ask the Doctors” section in which reader questions are answered by medical experts, and information on caring for your pet. The magazine was based on information from [[The Merck Manuals]] and reviewed by an independent board of medical professionals and patient advocacy organizations.
In 2006 the magazine started a [[Spanish language in the United States|Spanish]] version.<ref name=prn>{{cite news|title=Your Health Now Magazine Launches Spanish Edition|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/your-health-now-magazine-launches-spanish-edition-55867702.html|accessdate=13 December 2015|work=PR Newswire|date=2 August 2006}}</ref>
